summary: I’m doing emergency commissions and donations at the moment to help me with a medical bill I recently received. I had to have an...
caption:
I’m doing emergency commissions and donations at the moment to help me with a medical bill I recently received. I had to have an emergency surgery on my mouth for a returning/spreading infection and my insurance really sucks so I’m asking for help to soften the blow hopefully. Currently, I live alone in an apartment with 2 jobs so I honestly can only do so much and had to ask for help on the first mandatory payment. They’ll be drafted from my bank each month and I already know I don’t have the money to shoulder another bill.

If you would like to help or support me could you please spread this around if you could, it would help me out a whole bunch, thank you super much!

(Each picture below my medical bill is an example of each commission I have referenced in order. Please also take into consideration that there might be a wait time due to my current health as well, but your commission will definitely come to you! Non-Splatoon commissions are more than welcome! NSFW okay 👌)

Patreon (This starts off as low as $1 if you would like to simply support my art here!)

Ko-Fi (each Ko-Fi fines 40¢ per $3 donation but this is still a good option, every cent counts either way!)

Paypal: Hidan517@hotmail.com (If you would be so kind as to donate here, its the only direct money source that won’t fine you, just make sure to set your payment as friends and family)
